ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR AI INTEGRATION:

This software integrates with third-party AI services (Groq, Claude, OpenAI) 
that have their own terms of service and privacy policies:

- Groq Terms: https://groq.com/terms-of-service/
- Claude Terms: https://www.anthropic.com/terms
- OpenAI Terms: https://openai.com/terms/

Users are responsible for compliance with these third-party terms when using 
AI features of this extension. The authors disclaim any liability for 
third-party service usage, availability, or content generated by AI services.

PRIVACY NOTICE:

This extension processes text content selected by users for text-to-speech 
conversion and optional AI explanation services. By design:

- No user data is collected without explicit consent
- Selected text may be sent to AI services if explanation features are used
- All processing is optional and user-controlled
- No persistent tracking or analytics without user consent
- All settings are stored locally in browser storage

Users should review and understand the privacy implications before using 
AI explanation features.